Chile’s Northern Electricity Grid Loses Power, Cooperativa Says

-- B y   H e l e n   M u r p h y
-- 
2011-06-19T15:58:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-19/chile-s-northern-electricity-grid-loses-power-cooperativa-says.html
As much as 70 percent of  Chile ’s
northern electricity grid was knocked out this morning,  Radio
Cooperativa  reported.  Power is slowly returning and the government is
investigating the cause, Cooperativa said, citing Mining
Minister  Laurence Golborne .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Helen Murphy in Bogota at 
 hmurphy1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dale Crofts at 
 dcrofts@bloomberg.net . 